title: Community, Location, Quality Living. It All Starts Here
posting_body: ['Our Community is A+', 'Welcome Home to Elevate at Red Rocks Apartment Homes', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Elevate at Red Rocks', '409 Zang Street, Lakewood, CO, 80228', 'Follow The Link', 'Below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1101 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Elevate at Red Rocks offers spacious one, two, and three bedroom apartments nestled in the foothills of the Rocky Mountains.', 'Only minutes away from downtown Denver, the community is in close proximity to numerous parks, shopping destinations, restaurants, and entertainment.', 'Residents can enjoy a dip in the pool, take a stroll with their dog around the community or take a short drive to enjoy the nearby countryside.', 'Whether it’s the fast pace of city life or a relaxing mountain atmosphere you’re looking for, Elevate at Red Rocks has something for everyone.', 'Features', '- Air Conditioner Balcony Ceiling Fan Heat Patio Washer/Dryer', '- Disposal', '- Window Coverings', '- Dishwasher', '- Refrigerator', '- Garage', '- Cable/Satellite', '- Package Receiving', '- Range', 'Community Amenities', '- Free Weights Available', '- On-Site Maintenance', '- Playground', '- Storage', '- Garage', '- On-Site Management', '- Carport', '- Accept Credit Card Payments', '- Business Center Clubhouse Fitness Center Night Patrol Pets Allowed Pool TV Lounge Online Payments Available', '- Public Transportation', '- Accepts Electronic Payments and Service Requests', '- Street Parking', 'Pet Policy', 'Some breed restrictions ask for details', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5 times the monthly rent', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'ZLAUNd3K']
